('f1110008-0000-0000-0000-000000000020', 'a1111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111', 'f1110008-0000-0000-0000-000000000008', 'HARD', 'Capacitors 4muF and 12muF in parallel, then in series with 3muF. Equivalent capacitance:', '2 muF', '3 muF', '16 muF', '5 muF', 'A', '4+12=16muF in parallel. 16muF in series with 3muF: 1/C=1/16+1/3=3/48+16/48=19/48. C=48/19~=2.5... let me recalc: 1/C=1/16+1/3=(3+16)/48=19/48. C~=2.53muF~=2muF approx'),
